==Bosnian==
===Etymology===
From Turkish [[budala#Turkish|budala]] < Arabic plural ''abdāl'' of singular {{ARchar|[[بدل|بَدَل]]}} (''badal'') or {{ARchar|[[بديل|بَدِيل]]}} (''badīl'')
===Noun===
'''budala''' {{f}} {{s}} ({{p}}: '''budale''')
:Note:  ''Although the word itself is feminine, it can also be applied to a masculine person without any change.''
#[[fool]]
#[[idiot]]
#[[simpleton]]
====Synonyms====
*[[abdal#Bosnian|abdal]]
*[[luđak#Bosnian|luđak]]
*[[glupak#Bosnian|glupak]]
